{
  "stem": "12810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But probably if my stepbrother heard that-- that one, you know, he will be upset.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, you know, when my brother write me a letter and come to Australia and I help him to come here-- because like my mother teach me, it's not his fault.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's your brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was about 20, 22 at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to him, you want your mother to come out after you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, yes, please.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't like her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I never like her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I said to my husband, I said, listen darling, that's his mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother teach me to like him, so I think we should try to bring her out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Australia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was sure if he-- if she come, she make miserable my life again, you know, even to see her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not to live with her, but to see her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I said to my darling husband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, but we have to do it for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we fixed it up the papers and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got a deed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we sent the ticket to the boat and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then she get a cancer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the day when she should come out, she died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the God-- I believe God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, she don't-- the God wanted to I should make the sacrifice to show Him what type of person I am.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I bring her out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he don't let her come to make my life miserable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So after she told you the news of your father, did she go back to her house?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after the war, she was fighting off that-- that property.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
